01:15:01,760 --> 01:15:03,440
compiled by Richard Lin,

1353
01:15:03,440 --> 01:15:06,800
and we'll start with this one, Woburn 1969,

1354
01:15:06,800 --> 01:15:11,680
which apparently reported an IQ score of 86 from Nigeria.

1355
01:15:11,680 --> 01:15:14,080
And here it is, the meaning and stability

1356
01:15:14,080 --> 01:15:17,120
of Raven's matrices test among Africans,

1357
01:15:17,120 --> 01:15:18,960
and let's read a little of that.

1358
01:15:18,960 --> 01:15:22,080
This paper aims to clarify our understanding of factors

1359
01:15:22,080 --> 01:15:24,640
affecting African scores on ability tests,

1360
01:15:24,640 --> 01:15:26,800
Raven's matrices in particular.

1361
01:15:26,800 --> 01:15:28,720
Though the main burden is theoretical,

1362
01:15:28,720 --> 01:15:31,280
some fresh data from Nigeria will be shown.

1363
01:15:31,280 --> 01:15:34,320
During 1965, a testing program was carried out

1364
01:15:34,320 --> 01:15:36,320
among factory workers in Nigeria.

1365
01:15:36,320 --> 01:15:39,360
The results from 86 men will be reported here.

1366
01:15:39,360 --> 01:15:41,760
They were tested individually in English or Pidgin

1367
01:15:41,760 --> 01:15:44,880
by the author with the aid of a trained Nigerian assistant.

1368
01:15:44,880 --> 01:15:48,080
Among the test battery were Raven's progressive matrices

1369
01:15:48,080 --> 01:15:50,560
and an adapted embedded figures test,

1370
01:15:50,560 --> 01:15:52,960
which with an index of educational attainment

1371
01:15:52,960 --> 01:15:54,560
are explained by Woburn.

1372
01:15:54,560 --> 01:15:56,000
Six months after the tests,

1373
01:15:56,000 --> 01:15:58,160
each man was given the matrices again.

1374
01:15:58,160 --> 01:15:59,760
