1382
01:16:17,280 --> 01:16:18,560
is significantly greater

1383
01:16:18,560 --> 01:16:21,760
than between the initial matrices testing and EFT,

1384
01:16:21,760 --> 01:16:23,600
even though in the former comparisons,

1385
01:16:23,600 --> 01:16:26,000
