1386
01:16:26,000 --> 01:16:28,800
Table one shows that the overall differences in retesting

1387
01:16:28,800 --> 01:16:31,280
were significant and suggests that improvements

1388
01:16:31,280 --> 01:16:34,800
were found particularly among the lower initial scorers.

1389
01:16:34,800 --> 01:16:38,000
Taken with the improved EFT correlation in table two,

1390
01:16:38,000 --> 01:16:40,560
a strong case can be made that the second testing

1391
01:16:40,560 --> 01:16:42,480
gave a distinctly more valid measure

1392
01:16:42,480 --> 01:16:46,160
of whatever abilities the matrices and EFT involve.

1393
01:16:46,160 --> 01:16:48,960
So to quickly summarize, in 1965,

1394
01:16:48,960 --> 01:16:52,000
researchers gave 86 Nigerian factory workers

1395
01:16:52,000 --> 01:16:53,840
the Raven's Progressive Matrices Test

1396
01:16:53,840 --> 01:16:56,160
and then gave it to them again six months later.

1397
01:16:56,160 --> 01:16:57,600
The second time they took the test,

1398
01:16:57,600 --> 01:16:59,040
