1399
01:16:59,040 --> 01:17:00,640
and the results better correlated

1400
01:17:00,640 --> 01:17:03,200
with another test they took called the EFT.

1401
01:17:03,200 --> 01:17:05,680
And table one here shows both mean results,

1402
01:17:05,680 --> 01:17:10,400
15.9 the first time, increasing to 18.73 the second time.

1403
01:17:10,400 --> 01:17:14,240
What is missing here, you may have noticed, is an IQ score.

1404
01:17:14,240 --> 01:17:16,640
