1412
01:17:38,160 --> 01:17:40,720
and Lin, or whoever typed up his data,

1413
01:17:40,720 --> 01:17:42,880
accidentally wrote the number of test subjects

1414
01:17:42,880 --> 01:17:44,480
in the IQ field.

1415
01:17:44,480 --> 01:17:47,360
