1422
01:18:04,960 --> 01:18:07,280
for a sample of 86 adult men.

1423
01:18:07,280 --> 01:18:09,760
Their mean score was 15.9.

1424
01:18:09,760 --> 01:18:11,600
And then he later claims that this equates

1425
01:18:11,600 --> 01:18:13,680
to an IQ of 64.

1426
01:18:13,680 --> 01:18:16,240
Now, there are several lies by omission here.

1427
01:18:16,240 --> 01:18:21,120
Firstly, Wober 1969 did not report a mean score of 15.9.

1428
01:18:21,120 --> 01:18:23,680
It reported a mean score of 15.9

1429
01:18:23,680 --> 01:18:27,120
and a mean score of 18.73.

1430
01:18:27,120 --> 01:18:29,920
It showed how scores go up with retesting.

1431
01:18:29,920 --> 01:18:32,080
And additionally, it claims that a strong case

1432
01:18:32,080 --> 01:18:34,000
can be made that the second testing

1433
01:18:34,000 --> 01:18:35,840
gave a distinctly more valid measure

1434
01:18:35,840 --> 01:18:39,040
of whatever abilities the matrices and EFT involve.

1435
01:18:39,040 --> 01:18:41,680
