as representative of a country,

1447
01:19:07,840 --> 01:19:11,280
which at the time had a population of 50 million people,

1448
01:19:11,280 --> 01:19:12,880
is... rubbish.

1449
01:19:14,160 --> 01:19:15,040
Just rubbish.

1450
01:19:15,680 --> 01:19:17,680
