1461
01:19:49,520 --> 01:19:52,640
how items of the test are to be responded to,

1462
01:19:52,640 --> 01:19:55,600
and when the method reduces the anxiety of the subjects

1463
01:19:55,600 --> 01:19:57,120
about being tested,

1464
01:19:57,120 --> 01:20:00,160
then the results obtained from the administration of the test

1465
01:20:00,160 --> 01:20:02,560
are remarkably different from those that result

1466
01:20:02,560 --> 01:20:05,280
from administration in which the same test is presented

1467
01:20:05,280 --> 01:20:07,200
in the same way to all testees,

1468
01:20:07,200 --> 01:20:09,440
regardless of their cultural origin.

1469
01:20:09,440 --> 01:20:12,480
It goes on to detail how a researcher named Pons

1470
01:20:12,480 --> 01:20:15,200
