1479
01:20:38,400 --> 01:20:40,800
aren't necessarily going to be all that familiar

1480
01:20:40,800 --> 01:20:43,680
with taking academic tests, not to generalize,

1481
01:20:43,680 --> 01:20:45,600
and if you want more accurate results,

1482
01:20:45,600 --> 01:20:48,880
it might be worth taking the time to actually explain to them

1483
01:20:48,880 --> 01:20:51,120
what it is that they're being expected to do.

1484
01:20:51,680 --> 01:20:52,960
Now, Crawford Knott claims

1485
01:20:52,960 --> 01:20:54,720
that the different method of presentation

1486
01:20:54,720 --> 01:20:57,040
